snippet.title: Atomic Heart Official Gameplay Trailer | The Game Awards 2022
snippet.description:
The high anticipated sci-fi Soviet shooter gets an all new trailer. Featuring over-the-top robotic enemies to the aggressive guitar riffs of Mick Gordon.
